information: The company ESCO - EUROPEAN SALT COMPANY GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 2001, which operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industry. It also operates in the Fish, Dietary and organic foods, Condiments, extracts and spices, and Raw materials for construction and public works industries. It is based in Hannover, Germany.
